CatDescriptText: The Musicians Club, located on Wylie Avenue in the Lower Hill District, had a stage with a "MC" monogram painted above it.
TitMainTitle: Five-piece band with Fred Tooks on piano, Thay Whitely on saxophone, Jim "Jimmy" Swan on trumpet, Leon Lonen on bass, and Al Smart on drums, performing on stage at the Musicians Club
